Paper: hep-th/9905105

Date: 1999-05-14

Title: Yangian symmetry in the Non Linear Schrodinger hierarchy

Authors: M. Mintchev, E. Ragoucy, P. Sorba and Ph Zaugg

Comments: LaTeX2e, 23 pages

Integrable SystemsJournal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) 5885-5900

We study the Yangian symmetry of the multicomponent Quantum NonlinearSchrodinger hierarchy in the framework of the Quantum Inverse ScatteringMethod. We give an explicit realization of the Yangian generators in terms ofthe deformed oscillators algebra which naturally occurs in this framework.